name: Mad Men: Season 2
description: Returning for its second season, the Golden Globe®-winning series for Best TV drama and actor will continue to blur the lines between truth and lies, perception and reality. The world of Mad Men is moving in a new direction -- can Sterling Cooper keep up? Meanwhile the private life of Don Draper becomes complicated in a new way. What is the cost of his secret identity?

name: The World of the Married - Season 1
description: Her perfect life was shattered to pieces.

name: Honey Bunny Ka Jholmaal - Season 1
description: In a cozy house in the town owned by a young lady there lives 2 cats, a parrot and a watch dog who are the sweetest and the meekest pets ever but the moment the young lady leaves home, the cats becomes super mischievous, the parrot becomes super talkative and the poor dog goes super frantic.

name: The Last Narc - Season 1
description: In 1985, American DEA agent Enrique “Kiki” Camarena was kidnapped, tortured, and murdered by Mexico’s most notorious drug lords. Thirty-five years later, three former cartel insiders share unprecedented details. This is the story of Camarena, the drug cartel he infiltrated, and the narc who risked everything to discover the truth.

name: Laakhon Mein Ek - Season 2
description: Dr Shreya is posted in Sitlapur village to conduct a cataract camp. But the villagers aren't the biggest believers in Government healthcare, the supplies aren't separate from the politics, and the staff isn't the dream team one would desire. Dr Shreya keeps fighting the system, but the question remains whether she will change the system or will the system change her?

name: Carnival Row - Season 2
description: Love. Murder. Conspiracy. Revolution. When mysterious killings inflame tensions between the Faefolk and their Human oppressors, each denizen of “Carnival Row” must choose who they are and how to act.

name: Unforgettable, Season 4
description: A chance meeting puts a female ex-cop in touch with her former boyfriend, a New York City police detective, who convinces her to use her extraordinary memory to solve crimes.

name: All or Nothing: Manchester City  -  Season 1
description: In this ground-breaking docu-series, follow Manchester City behind the scenes throughout their Premier League winning, record-breaking ‘17-18 season. Get an exclusive look into one of the best global sports clubs, including never-before-seen dressing room footage with legendary coach Pep Guardiola, and delve into the players’ lives off and on the pitch.

name: Calle y Poché: No Labels - Season 1
description: At the peak of their successful careers as content creators, Calle and Poché return to Colombia to reunite with their families, their group of friends, and confront the challenges of their romantic relationship combined with their individual ambitions.

name: Lucky Romance (Hindi) - Season 1
description: An intelligent and practical CEO, Je Soo-ho, falls in love with a superstitious woman, Shim Bo-nui, who is burdened with many personal problems.

name: Comicstaan - Season 3
description: Your favourite show is back! In its third season, Comicstaan is back with 4 judges, 7 mentors, 2 hosts and 8 new contestants. Watch all episodes to find out who takes home the title this year.

name: The Mens Club - New Chapter
description: The Men’s Club takes us on a journey of four friends surrounded by women, business and the hassles of the city.

name: My First Love (Hindi) - Season 1
description: Yaprak has built a colorful world without the girly things and with these four guys beside her. One day this world changes with Barış coming into her life in a mysterious way. This change takes her to a discovery of her and the girls' world. Now she has to make a choice. She'll have to choose either the prince in shining armor or the hero with the dimples.

name: High School (Hindi) - Season 1
description: Based on Tegan and Sara Quin's best-selling memoir, High School is a story about finding your own identity—a journey made even more complicated when you have a twin whose own struggle and self-discovery so closely mimics your own. Told through a backdrop of ‘90s grunge and rave culture, the series weaves between the memories of two sisters growing up together.

name: Prime Rewind: Inside The Boys - Season 1
description: "The Boys" Official After Show, hosted by Aisha Tyler and featuring the creators and cast from the series, including Karl Urban (Butcher), Jack Quaid (Hughie), Antony Starr (Homelander), Erin Moriarty (Starlight), Laz Alonso (Mother's Milk), Tomer Capon (Frenchie), Karen Fukuhara (Kimiko), and showrunner Eric Kripke

name: Luden - Season 1
description: Inspired by true events, the gangster epic LUDEN tells the rise of the Nutella Gang, the most famous pimp cartel in Hamburg's legendary Reeperbahn during the 1980s. The unusual cartel turns the rough red-light district in St. Pauli into a glamourous place, but it is also the beginning of a power struggle with the established pimps of the GMBH.

name: The Boarding School: Las Cumbres - Season 3
description: Three months after the terrible events that ended Paz' life, Amaia is sure that the mysteries surrounding the boarding school are not solved. Determined to get to the bottom of the mystery, Amaia implicates Zoe, a new student. Soon, the group is involved in disappearances and horrible crimes inside the convent walls. A trial by fire to their friendships.

name: Dawson's Creek, Season 2
description: As Dawson struggles to accept his parents’ shattered marriage, life for him and his friends is changed forever by the romances, revelations and tragedies that follow some newcomers to Capeside.

name: Panic - Season 1
description: In the forgotten town of Carp, Texas, Panic is the only way out. Every summer the graduating seniors risk their lives competing in a series of challenges for the chance to win life-changing money. After the death of two players the stakes – and danger—have never been higher. This summer twenty-three players will enter the game. All of them will be changed. Only one will win. Let the games begin.

name: Written in the Stars - Season 1
description: Written in the Stars is an astrological dating show. There are twelve episodes in which a single person, who represents one of the zodiac signs, is introduced to four bachelors or bachelorettes with whom they have different astral compatibilities. Chatting and chemistry: everything can be a sign of what the stars want. After the dates, it's time to make a decision: listen to or ignore the stars?

name: LOV3 - Temporada 01
description: Os irmãos SOFIA (24), BETO (24) e ANA (33) se recusam a experimentar amor e sexo como seus pais. E isso se torna ainda mais forte quando a mãe deles resolve abandonar o casamento de trinta anos. A separação é o ponto de partida para que os três reavaliem as suas próprias escolhas emocionais — e a capacidade de cuidarem um dos outros enquanto tentam não sufocar quem são de verdade.

name: The Last Ship: The Complete Third Season
description: The crew of the Nathan James shifting their attention to Asia after President Michener hears rumblings that the Chinese leader has been hoarding the "Scott cure" instead of distributing it to the people in the region. Michener sends Chandler to a global summit to investigate this allegation, as well as rumors of a possible mutation of the original virus that has caused a fresh outbreak in Japan.

name: After the Rain
description: Akira Tachibana(17) used to be the ace of a track club, but gave up running due to her injury. Masami Kondo(45) is a manager at a family restaurant called Garden, where Akira works. This story is set in a seaside town, and depicts a girl who stopped at a cross-point in her youth, and a man who reached a turning point of life. Everybody wants that moment where they get fraught with great emotions.

name: Kaali Peeli Tales- Season 1
description: ‘Kaali Peeli Tales’ is an anthology of six bitter-sweet short stories with themes like infidelity, open marriage, homosexuality, divorce and love in the times of social media. Watch the resolution of each story taking place in the iconic Kaali-Peeli taxi only on Amazon miniTV.

name: Payback: Money and Power - Season 1
description: Eun Yong, a money business titan and an affluent financial capitalist, has been living a life of a recluse in the pastures of Mongolia. Eun returns to Korea when his nephew Tae-chun and his late benefactor's daughter Joon-gyeong enlists his help. He prepares for war against corrupt powers to protect his beloved family and to avenge the death of a dear old friend.

name: The Lake - Season 1
description: A biting comedy with Jordan Gavaris, Julia Stiles and Madison Shamoun. After a divorce leaves Justin’s life in disarray, he must pick-up the pieces. This includes reconnecting with Billie, the daughter he gave up for adoption. Justin hopes summer at the lake will bring them closer. It does the opposite until they team up to take back the family cottage from Justin’s step-sister Maisy-May.

name: Darr Ke Uss Paar - Season 1
description: This series presents tales dealing with frightening, psychologically disturbing and often paranormal true or rumored nightmares. All the stories are tied together with a human emotional journey.

name: The End of Love - Season 1
description: Tamara, an edgy feminist philosopher, rediscovers a past she thought she had left behind.

name: Veronica Mars Season 2
description: In the wealthy, seaside community of Neptune, the rich and powerful make the rules. They own the town and the high school, and they desperately try to keep their dirty little secrets just that...secret. Unfortunately for them, there's Veronica Mars, a smart, fearless 18-year-old apprentice private investigator dedicated to solving the town's toughest mysteries. During the day, high school senio...

name: Comicstaan Semma Comedy Pa - Season 1
description: Aspiring comedians compete to become the future of funny in Tamil stand-up comedy. Mentored by the biggest Tamil comedians, find out who will be crowned the winner of Comicstaan Semma Comedy Pa!

name: Covert Affairs
description: Covert Affairs stars Golden Globe®-nominated Piper Perabo as Annie Walker, a young CIA operative whose exceptional linguistic skills make her invaluable to the Agency in missions that span the globe. While quickly becoming a seasoned field operative, Annie’s career continues to intrude on her personal life, and she strives to for the perfect balance of "normal" with her high-octane adventures...

name: The Chelsea Detective S01
description: In a world where appearance is everything, DI Max Arnold has a keen eye for detail and isn't afraid to delve inside Chelsea's hidden nooks and crannies in order to crack a case.

name: Akkad Bakkad Rafu Chakkar - Season 1
description: The “good life” is just one scam away. This thought takes root in the minds of two friends Bhargav and Siddhant after they read countless news stories of bank scams that have happened in the country and that a total of seventy-one thousand five hundred crores has been scammed. Together they devise a plan to open India’s first fake bank. Will they get away or will they get caught?

name: 1883 Season 1
description: Follows the Dutton family on a journey west through the Great Plains toward the last bastion of untamed America.

name: The Girlfriend Experience
description: The third installment of "The Girlfriend Experience" is set amidst the London tech scene and focuses on Iris, a neuroscience major. As she begins to explore the transactional world of The Girlfriend Experience, Iris quickly learns that client sessions provide her with a compelling edge in the tech world, and vice versa...until, that is, she begins to question whether her actions are driven by f...

name: GRIND - SEASON 1
description: New episode every Friday!  Born to a single mother in the slum of Lagos, Tare-ela takes up the offer from her childhood friend Edesiri to become a stripper in order to feed her family and cover the fees of her 10 year old sister. We walk with them through relationships, the weight of family expectations, the failure of old dreams and the forging of new ones as they go about their grind.

name: Work Later, Drink Now S1
description: Three single women in 30s gather and talk about everyday life from work to love. Nothing is more important to them than enjoying a drink after work.

name: Super Bheem - Season 1
description: Super Bheem is the valiant superhero of all the galaxies combined and embarks on many adventurous journeys through mythical lands.

name: AFSOS - Season 1
description: A suicidal man and a deadly assassin encounter the world of immortality in this black comedy suspense thriller.

name: Eken Babu - Season 1
description: Hoichoi Originals presents ‘Eken Babu’ featuring a man with a quirky persona, who lands up in an apartment in Bangalore, much to the annoyance of its residents.

name: With Love - Season 2
description: WITH LOVE is a romantic dramedy centered around siblings Lily and Jorge Diaz as they navigate big life changes and rely on their equally big family to get them through their thirties. From weddings and new loves to heartbreak and good old-fashioned family drama, season two shows Lily and Jorge grow like we've never seen them before.

name: The Expanse - Season 6
description: Holden and the crew of the Rocinante fight alongside the Combined Fleet of Earth and Mars to protect the Inner Planets from Marco Inaros and his Free Navy's campaign of death and destruction. Meanwhile, on a distant planet beyond the Rings, a new power rises.

name: James May: Oh Cook - Season 1
description: James May is not a chef. But that’s the whole point: you don’t need to be a brilliant cook to make delicious food. Transporting us to the Far East, the Med, and the local pub – all from the comfort of a home economist’s kitchen – he’ll knock up delicious recipes that you can actually make yourself, with ingredients you can actually buy. And all without the usual television cooking format trickery.

name: Minus One Season 1
description: Riya (Aisha Ahmed) and Varun (Ayush Mehra) used to live together as a couple in New Delhi. but then they broke up. Now they live together as flatmates.

name: Secrets Of Sinauli - Season 1
description: The discovery of a 4,000-year-old war chariot in Sinauli, Uttar Pradesh, has historians questioning if the wars in Indian mythology were true events. Presented by Neeraj Pandey, uncover the mysteries behind the excavations with Ma

name: INUYASHIKI LAST HERO
description: Ichiro Inuyashiki was a boring office worker living a life shunned by his family and coworkers. One night, a UFO crashed into him, and his body was rebuilt into a powerful robot. A high school student named Hiro Shishigami was also involved in the same accident, and he begins to use his new powers to enable his darkest impulses. Is man's true nature good or evil?

name: Utopia - Season 1
description: Utopia is a conspiracy thriller that follows a group of young fans who come together when they discover that the conspiracy in an elusive comic, Utopia, is real. The comic foretells the demise of humanity and the world as we know it, thrusting this group of underdogs to embark on a high-stakes twisted adventure to use what they uncover to save themselves, each other and ultimately humanity.

name: The King of Pigs - Season 1
description: Two friends in the past were victims of serious school bulling. One could not resist his trauma, and becomes a serial killer, walking in the path of revenge. Another one tries his best to overcome the trauma and becomes a police detective. He now faces tragic fate to risk his life to capture the serial killer.

name: The Originals: Season 4
description: For more than a millennium, the Original vampire-werewolf hybrid Klaus Mikaelson and his brother Elijah have fought for their family no matter the cost, but their actions have spawned a legion of enemies. Now surrounded by foes, they enact a brutal strategy that will turn even their friends and family against them, thus fulfilling the prophecy itself and setting the course for season four.

name: The Penthouse: War in Life Season 2
description: After successfully framing OH Yoonhee for murder, CHEON Seojin and JOO Dantae decide to get married. Their engagement party is interrupted by OH Yoonhee and HA Yooncheol, who have just come back from the United States. As the secrets unveil, the relationships among the people at Hera Palace are entangled, yet another mysterious figure appears and confronts them.

name: Mind The Malhotras - Season 2
description: In Mind the Malhotras Season 2, Rishabh works on a merger that will make him a millionaire. But as Shefali embarks on a career as an online Chef and begins to rack up followers, the demands of being a family clash with individual goals. Rishabh and Shefali need therapy more than ever. Chaos ensues when rather than acknowledging this, they seek out Dr. Gulfam behind each other's back.

name: Nip/Tuck - Season 1
description: Hotshot plastic surgeon Christian Troy enjoys all the perks of the successful and growing Miami practice that he shares with his best friend, Sean McNamara. But years of selling a phony image have taken their toll on Sean.

name: History's Greatest Heists with Pierce Brosnan - Season 1
description: Uncovering the meticulous planning, daring execution and shocking aftermath behind some of the most elaborate real-life heists in history.

name: Truth Seekers - Season 1
description: Broadband installer by day, paranormal investigator by night, Gus is annoyed to be partnered with “noob” Elton, but comes to appreciate having someone along for the ride as they uncover a spike in supernatural activity. They’re soon joined by Astrid, who has ghost problems of her own, and the gang embark upon creating a ghost-hunting YouTube channel, uncovering a terrifying conspiracy as they go.

name: Secrets of the Koh-i-noor - Season 1
description: A historical journey traces the steps of the world's most fabled diamond -- the Koh-i-noor. Explore the insatiable lust for the famous diamond, which shaped the course of history through significant bloody wars, empowered rulers and ruined dynasties.

name: Switch (Hindi) - Season 1
description: A prosecutor and a conman work together to catch the bad guys who know their way around the law.

name: Inside Edge - Season 1
description: Inside Edge is the story of the Mumbai Mavericks, a T20 cricket franchise playing in the Powerplay League. Set in a landscape of conflicting interests, where selfishness is almost a virtue, where sex, money, and power are mere means to an end, Inside Edge is a story that pulls no punches, minces no words, and takes no prisoners. Come witness the game behind the game.

name: Welcome to Waikiki - Season 2
description: Protecting the guesthouse against bankruptcy. At all costs.

name: Bang Bang Baby - Season 1
description: 1986. Alice is a 16-year-old girl living in a small town in the North of Italy. Her life suddenly changes when she finds out her long-deceased father is still alive. Alice begins a descent into Milan's criminal underbelly, diving into the dangerous world of the ‘ndrangheta out of love for her father. By the time she tries to get out of that world, it might already be too late.

name: Goliath - Season 2
description: Billy McBride returns to criminal defense, taking on a grisly double murder case. His client is a 16-year-old boy, and Billy’s damn sure he’s innocent. Billy, Patty, and the team fervently build their case in the seedy underworld of Los Angeles. As the murders’ true culprits come to light, the implications reach as far as the mayoral race — and the city’s preeminent billionaire developer.

name: Season 8
description: A multi-generational comedy set in the 1980s about what it's like to grow up in a loud, warm, and slightly troubled family—the Goldbergs. Our narrator recalls his past with an overbearing mother, a hot-headed father, a rebellious sister, a hysterical brother, and a courteous grandfather.

name: Big Issue (Hindi) - Season 1
description: Seok Joo is given a second chance. He works for Soo Hyun to fight despair in the world fueled by Big Issues.

name: Breathe: Into The Shadows – Season 2
description: J’s existence and ideology re-emerge as he sets out to finish what he started, leading Avinash to confront his merging dual identity. But this time around, he has a new partner-in-crime, Victor. Kabir Sawant must now fight the battle of his life as he protects the society that has become a victim in the endgame of this crazed saga.

name: Paper Girls - Season 1
description: Four young friends’ paper routes are disrupted on Hell Day 1988, when they unknowingly time travel to 2019. While searching for a way home, they clash with members of two time-jumping factions at war, and must come face-to-face with their adult selves and learn how to work together to save the world.

name: The Great Escapists - Season 1
description: In this season Richard Hammond and Tory Belleci use what’s left of their shipwreck to survive and thrive. Using their engineering know how, the boys try to escape the island and even make their island life better. From a fully working tank to a three-story treehouse on the seafront, life is pretty sweet. But will their inventions help them escape, or keep them stuck forever in paradise?

name: The Head of Joaquín Murrieta
description: [Original audio in "Español Latinamerica"] Greed took over California because of the gold rush. It made people thirsty for wealth and land. There, in the newly drawn border between Mexico and the US, a lawless war for control, fueled by the anger and xenophobia of the past war, is led by a group of immigrants who join forces to create the myth of the Latin Robin Hood: Joaquín Murrieta.

name: Laakhon Mein Ek - Season 2
description: Dr. Shreya is posted in Sitlapur village to conduct a cataract camp but challenges begin unfolding one after the other. She keeps fighting the system but the question remains whether she will change the system or the system will change her?

name: Claws: Season 1
description: Set in a South Florida nail salon, CLAWS is a midnight-dark, wickedly funny meditation on female badness which follows the rise of five diverse and treacherous Florida manicurists at the Nail Artisan of Manatee County Salon, where there is a lot more going on than silk wraps and pedicures. At the center is salon owner Desna, her mentally ill twin brother, Dean, and her staff of four friends.

name: The Penthouse: War in Life Season 3
description: Once the residents from Hera Place are released from prison, SHIM Suryeon and OH Yoonhee form an alliance with CHEON Seojin to take down JOO Dantae. Soon, BAEK Joonki enters the picture as an old friend of JOO Dantae. What secret does he hold on JOO Dantae?

name: The Office S01
description: Ricky Gervais co-writes, directs and stars in the original British version of The Office that became a worldwide comedy phenomenon.

name: Killing Eve Season 2
description: Picking up where Series 1 left off, Killing Eve 2 follows Eve Polastri as she navigates the fallout of stabbing love-drunk psychopath and career assassin, Villanelle. The two are drawn ever closer as MI6 are tasked with an even bigger threat than the likes of one lone killer. Under Carolyn’s watch, Eve manipulates her complex relationship with Villanelle to recruit her for a crucial operation.

name: Breaking Point: Air Force Academy - Season 1
description: The Air Force Academy at Dundigul, Hyderabad, India, is a one-stop station for churning out men of mettle.

name: Absentia - Season 3
description: Season 3 picks up after the Dramatic events of Season 2 with Emily nearing the end of her FBI suspension. Everything is upended when one of Nick’s criminal cases threatens the lives of Emily’s family. Her efforts to unravel a dangerous conspiracy take Emily to Europe, testing her like never before and forcing her to learn to trust and love again as she finally realizes her true place in the world.

name: Come And Hug Me (Tamil) - Season 1
description: A dramatic drama depicting the love of a man and a woman whose lives are linked because of a murder since young age. Despite an unfortunate destiny and the stigma and pains, they will try to be happy and heal their wounds.

name: Covert Affairs
description: Season five of the hit espionage series picks up with CIA operative Annie (Golden Globe®-nominated Piper Perabo, “Looper”) returning to the Agency after having faked her death to go deep undercover to find a traitor to the CIA.

name: Le Mans: Racing is Everything Season 1
description: The 24 Hours of Le Mans is a motor race like no other. Taking place in France each year, it is an endurance test for drivers and cars that literally takes 24 hours to complete. Traveling from Kuala Lumpur to the Côte D’Azur, shot in breathtaking 4K and with unprecedented access to six of the teams competing for glory, Le Mans: Racing is Everything is motorsport as you’ve never seen it before.

name: Black Sails: Season 1
description: BLACK SAILS tells the story of Captain Flint, the most brilliant and feared pirate of his day, who takes on a fast-talking addition to his crew who goes by the name John Silver. Threatened with extinction on all sides, they fight for the survival of New Providence Island, a debauched paradise teeming with pirates, prostitutes, thieves and fortune seekers, a place defined by both its enlightene...

name: SKY Castle
description: How do the wives of the richest families in Korea, those who have wealth, honor, and power, prepare for university entrance exams? We see their desperate struggles as they try to create the next generation of lawyers and doctors. This is a comical, satirical drama that thoroughly looks into the social desires of Korean families.

name: She Was Pretty (Tamil) - Season 1
description: When Ji Sung-Joon was young, he was ugly. As he grew up, he began to have an attractive appearance. When Kim Hye-Jin was young, she was pretty. As she grew up, she became ugly. Ji Sung-Joon tries to find his first love.

name: MILF Manor - Season 1
description: Hot single moms dive into a unique dating experience where they hope to find their -- much younger -- soulmates, but a shocking twist turns their world upside down.

name: The Expanse - Season 3
description: Season 3 opens as the war between Earth and Mars ignites across the solar system and the terrifying next phase in the evolution of the Protomolecule threatens the very existence of humanity.

name: Dexter Season 5
description: Dexter grieves his loss and tries to stay one step ahead of a suspicious Quinn and his own sister, while reluctantly guiding a near-victim (Julia Stiles) of a serial killer who sets out to get lethal revenge.

name: Coach Prime - Season 1
description: Coach Prime is the biggest story in college football. Watch how his coaching legacy was built in his third year at Jackson State as his team experiences a dramatic season that includes a water crisis, player injuries, and heightened expectations for his football team.

name: Outlaw - Season 1
description: The Chacha-Bhatija duo team up to expand their reign in Canada. These brown boys will soon become the town's outlaws.

name: The Kidnapping Day
description: Myeong-jun decides to kidnap Ro-hee to pay for his daughter's hospital bills. On his way, someone collapses before his car, which turns out to be Ro-hee. She doesn't remember anything, and Myeong-jun claims to be her dad and contacts her parents for the ransom but fails. He witnesses her parents' bodies being carried away at their house and leaves the scene. Ro-hee grows suspicious of Myeong-jun.

name: Modern Love Tokyo - Season 1
description: The Amazon Original series “Modern Love,” based on a column that appeared in The New York Times, has been distributed since 2019. Now “Modern Love” reboots with a new look in Tokyo as “Modern Love Tokyo.” The seven-episode anthology features a cast of leading actors and depicts various forms of “love,” such as love almost forgotten, love between sons and mothers, and love that transcends borders.

name: Transformers Robots In Disguise - Season 01
description: When a Cybertronian prison ship crashes on Earth, a new team of Autobots, led by Bumblebee, arrives to protect the planet and the galaxy - from hundreds of escaped Deception fugitives!

name: The Man in the High Castle - Season 2
description: After giving Joe the film, Juliana is forced to flee the fury of the Resistance while embarking on a new path to save her home from destruction. Joe confronts his absent father in Berlin, who is not as he seems. Smith wrestles with what to do about his ill son. Frank takes a gamble with his life in a bid to save Ed. Tagomi's life is turned upside down by his "travel" to an alternative world.

name: The Good Fight - Season 5
description: In the fifth season, Diane is forced to question whether it’s appropriate for her to help run an African American law firm with Liz when the firm loses two top lawyers. Meanwhile, Marissa and the firm become entangled with Hal Wackner, a regular Chicagoan who decides to open his own courtroom in the back of a copy shop.

name: Jimmy O. Yang: Guess How Much?
description: Jimmy O. Yang is back and better than ever in his follow up comedy special “Guess How Much?” where the actor/comedian talks about BTS, love languages, loser friends and negotiating with his Asian parents.

name: Flesh And Bone Season 1
description: This dark and gritty series follows young dancer, Claire, as she joins a prestigious New York City ballet company, and encounters the glamour and dysfunction of the ballet world.

name: Adulting - Season 1
description: Ray & Nikhat, as they try to make it through adulthood in their own unique way.

name: Desperately Seeking Soulmate: Escaping Twin Flames Universe - Season 1
description: Journalist Alice Hines delves into the world of Twin Flames Universe, an online group run by the captivating couple Jeff and Shaleia Divine. Their promise is to match members with their perfect partner, but after talking to former participants who describe the extreme lengths they have taken in order to claim their ‘twin flame,’ Alice soon discovers that the promise of true love comes at a price.

name: All or Nothing: Tottenham Hotspur
description: Go behind the scenes of Tottenham Hotspur Football Club during one of the most defining seasons in their history. Chairman Daniel Levy makes the mid-season decision to sack manager Mauricio Pochettino and hire José Mourinho. Players including Dele Alli, Heung-Min Son and Harry Kane fight to put the club amongst Europe’s elite against the backdrop of the global coronavirus crisis.

name: Shaitaan Haveli - Season 1
description: B-Grade filmmaker Hariman shows up to shoot his horror film at an old haveli. Freak occurrences make the crew realise that they're not just shooting a horror film but are soon going to be living one.

name: Love Kills: Madhumita Shukla Hatyakand - Season 1
description: This hard-hitting investigative series looks at the world of grisly murders in India. These stories of revenge, jealously and greed are broken down to reveal what actually happened to lead to a gruesome killing.

name: LOL - Hasse toh Phasse -Season 1
description: Hosted by Boman Irani and Arshad Warsi, 10 of India’s most entertaining comedians face a unique challenge - survive 6 hours together without laughing while doing whatever it takes to break the other contenders. In this one of a kind comedy battle, a laugh, giggle or smile could get you eliminated, and only the one that can keep a straight face to the finish will be crowned "Last One Laughing".

name: Mad Men: Season 4
description: Lionsgate's Mad Men, winner for Outstanding Drama Series, returns for a new season rife with possibilities. Last season stunned audiences with its cliffhanger finale, as Don Draper's professional and personal lives unexpectedly imploded. This year, Jon Hamm and the rest of the breakout ensemble continue to captivate us as they grapple with an uncertain new reality. Welcome to a Mad New World.

name: Chuck: The Complete Third Season
description: Zachary Levi stars as Chuck Bartowski, the Buy More electronics store computer geek who unwittingly becomes the government's most vital secret agent.

name: Argentine National Team, Road to Qatar - Season 1
description: Argentina National Football Team is getting ready for the World Cup and opens the door to behind-the-scenes. The qualifiers, the Copa América, the Finalissima and match preparation for Qatar as never seen before.

name: Yosi, the Regretful spy - Season 2
description: An undercover agent working for the Argentine intelligence services for some and a Mossad spy for others, Yosi Peres, is a double agent whose risks multiply. Tormented by the attack on AMIA and its cover-up, he confides his truth in a prestigious journalist, but his past shakes his present as Yosi gets double-crossed.

name: This Is Us Season 5
description: This Is Us chronicles the Pearson family across the decades and reveals how the tiniest events in our lives impact who we become and can transcend time, distance and even death.

name: Marimayam Season 1
description: The comedians represent satirical sketches describing the encounters the common man faces while visiting government institutions.

name: Goliath - Season 3
description: The unexpected death of an old friend leads Billy McBride to take a case in the drought-stricken Central Valley where he comes face-to-face with a new Goliath: a billionaire farmer and his sister and their scheme to steal California’s most valuable resource – water. As Billy and his team pursue the truth, old enemies and personal demons resurface forcing him to confront his own mortality.

name: GREEK SALAD - Season 1
description: Tom's and Mia's grandfather has just died. He's bequeathed them a building in Athens, where Mia is supposed to be studying. Tom joins her to oversee their inheritance and use the proceeds of its sale to launch his start-up based in NY... Only to discover that his sister has actually dropped out of school and that her anti-capitalist activities will complicate liquidating their joint bequest.

name: Money Mafia - Season 1
description: Money Mafia chronicles eight of the most intriguing and shocking con stories in India. The series delves into scams across the spectrum, ranging from Ponzi schemes and cyber fraud to call center scams and banking scandals.

name: African Wild - Season 1
description: In this journey, the secret world of Africa's largest and most-dangerous animals is revealed. From wild, grassy savannas to untouched beaches, these beasts show what it takes to survive in the elements and outwit natural enemies.

name: Star Trek: Discovery - Season 1
description: “Star Trek,” one of the most iconic and influential global television franchises, returns to television 50 years after it first premiered with STAR TREK: DISCOVERY. The series will feature a new ship, new characters, and new missions, while embracing the same ideology and hope for the future that inspired a generation of dreamers and doers.

name: Dark Mysteries: Anjaan Kahaniyaan - Season 1
description: Embark on a journey across India in the search of the unexplained. Through the series, we will track a range of mysteries covering themes like black magic, reincarnations, curses, ghost stories.

name: Tempted (Tamil) - Season 1
description: Love is just a game for Chaebol heir who agrees to a petty bet with his friends to seduce a college student - until he starts to fall for her.

name: Indu - Season 1
description: Marriage sets the ball rolling for a new stage of life. As Indu enters that phase in her life, will the dark secrets of her new home and new family endanger her life?

name: The Office
description: Season Three punches in with Jim Halpert's unexpected transfer to the Stamford office but will it punch out the closing of the Scranton branch?

name: The Girlfriend Experience - Season 2: Erica & Anna
description: Set against the upcoming 2018 U.S. midterm elections, season 2 tracks a complex relationship between Erica Myles, a finance director, and Anna Garner, a GFE provider.

name: Unpaused: Naya Safar - Season 1
description: Unpaused: Naya Safar continues to takes the legacy of the first anthology forward and yet again brings together 5 unique filmmakers - Nupur Asthana, Ayappa KM, Ruchir Arun, Shikha Makan and Nagraj Manjule - with new stories of hope, love, connections and second chances that celebrate the resilient human spirit in these uncertain times.

name: Hunter
description: Renegade cop Rick Hunter partners up with the equally tough-minded Sgt. McCall to crack down on Los Angeles criminals in this gutsy '80s cop drama.

name: Cheer Up (Tamil) - Season 1
description: A renowned college cheerleading squad is about to go under. But love and mysteries occur within the team.

name: TVF - Girliyapa Specials - Season 1
description: TVF

name: All or Nothing: New Zealand All Blacks - Season 1
description: For the first time ever, The New Zealand All Blacks rugby team, known as the winningest team in global sports history, allows cameras into their super secretive world to witness one of their most difficult seasons yet. Over four months, they face the demands of the most physically gruelling team sport on the planet to uphold a legacy of excellence and dominance that goes back well over a century.

name: Der Pass - I
description: When a body is found on the boundary stone on the Austro-German border, German police inspector Ellie Stocker and Austrian police inspector Gedeon Winter have to work together to unfold a mysterious series of cruel murders both north and south of the border German/Austrian border. The investigation in the snowed-in Alps is grinding them down, while both are going through private crises.

name: Dawson's Creek, Season 3
description: With college looming on the horizon, the teenagers of Capeside are caught in a revolving door of relationships and personal challenges that create obstacles and opportunities for the future.

name: Spain’s Elite Police: Beyond limits
description: For the first time in the history of the Spanish Police, a camera crew has exclusive access to the selection process for new members of the Special Group of Operations (G.E.O.), which lasts for more than 7 months. Dozens of police officers start, but only a few will finish the course.

name: Manjil Virinja Poovu Season 14
description: Evidences regarding Gireesh's murder point towards Anjana

name: Smallville: The Complete Second Season
description: The breakout hit "Smallville" returns for a second season. Young Clark Kent deals with all the challenges, hopes and desires of any other teenager ... while discovering and learning how to master his burgeoning superpowers.

name: The Confession - Season 1
description: When Patricia Hall vanishes from the small Yorkshire town of Pudsey, her husband Keith becomes a suspect, caught in a storm of rumour and suspicion. Only after a year, when Keith Hall falls in love with a beautiful stranger, does the terrible truth about his wife’s disappearance seem to emerge in a shocking series of twists and revelations.

name: Californication Season 6
description: When fast-living novelist Hank Moody left the literary haunts of New York for the pleasure seeking splendors of LA, he thought he'd have fame, fortune and the love of a good woman. Now his personal life is in shambles, his career is on the brink of self-destruction and he still just can't stop yielding to every temptation

name: Hiccups & Hookups Season 1 (Hindi)
description: A recently separated single mother, her commitment-phobic and successful younger brother, and her smart but confused teenaged daughter - all of whom make a sweet, unconventional family of three try their best to handle dating, relationships, and life.

name: Inside Edge - Season 3
description: Amidst the greatest show on earth: an India v/s Pakistan cricket series, the politics of Indian cricket is laid bare, its secrets unraveled and truths exposed. The stakes have never been higher, even as they are investigated for corruption, battle lines are drawn for TV rights, endorsement deals and the captaincy of the Indian team. But what is the limit to the price of power?

name: La Unidad - Season 1
description: In the middle of the night, officers from the Spanish, Moroccan and French police forces carry out a synchronized anti-jihadist operation in the three countries, resulting in the arrest of ISIS spiritual leader Al Salah Ghareeb. Retaliation looms, however, when Al Salah’s son Nadim announces in a video that the Caliphate will not only recover its leader but strike as never before on the peninsula.

name: Antormahal (Bengali) - Season 1
description: Riti and Indro's pursuit of parenthood unfolds a storm of traditional social and male conditioning that cause cracks in their marriage. In a tug of war of self-respect and ego, will Riti and Indro's relationship be the ultimate casualty?

name: Baahubali The Lost Legends - Season 3
description: A new season of Baahubali The Lost Legends begins as a new threat to Mahishmati arises from out of its dark past. Baahubali and Bhallaladeva find themselves exiled from their own kingdom and must journey a great distance to expose the hidden past of Mahishmati and regain the throne for the honor of Rajmata Sivagami!

name: Wakaalat From Home - Season 1
description: WFH (Wakaalat From Home) is the story of Sujin and Radhika’s divorce. It is not amicable with claims and counterclaims. The judge decides, this not being a critical case, to move their court hearing to Zoom. Over 10 court sessions, while the lockdown ensues, their divorce case will be heard, while their lawyers have designs of their own.

name: Uncoupled In Rio
description: After 7 years of marriage, a couple calls it quits, only to be forced to stay living in the same apartment until they can sort out their financial problems.

name: Shiny Happy People: Duggar Family Secrets - Season 1
description: A limited docuseries exposing the truth beneath the wholesome Americana surface of reality tv’s favorite mega-family, The Duggars, and the radical organization behind them: The Institute in Basic Life Principles. As details of the family and their scandals unfold, we realize they’re part of an insidious, much larger threat already in motion, with democracy itself in peril.

name: Chloe - Season 1
description: Becky’s lonely life is nothing like Chloe’s charmed one. One-time teenage friends, she now only watches Chloe through social media. When Chloe dies suddenly, Becky assumes a new identity and infiltrates the lives of Chloe's friends to find out why. As Sasha, she discovers the conflicting faces of Chloe, but is increasingly lost in her lies. Will she uncover the truth before she loses herself?

name: The Crimson Rivers - Season 1
description: In the series "The Crime Rivers", investigators Pierre Niémans and Camille Delauney must solve gruesome crimes. The two are always ordered to the scene of a crime when it involves particularly bizarre murders.

name: Lost Girl, Season 1
description: Having grown up thinking she was just a normal girl next door, Bo now suspects that there's nothing normal about her. After learning that she's a Succubus, a mythical being that drains its sex partners of life, Bo fights to control her powers while searching for the truth about her mysterious past.

name: The Forgotten Army - Azaadi ke liye - Season 1
description: The Forgotten Army is a true epic war series about the Indian soldiers from the Azad Hind Fauj who marched 3,884 kms from Singapore to Delhi to free their country from the British. Led by Netaji Subhash Chandra Bose, they fought against their size and scale but were labelled by the then ruling establishment as traitors. Experience an action packed series recreate this momentous juncture in history

name: Beyond Evil
description: In most popular police-centered stories, the protagonists are detectives investigating violent crimes. However, most officers work at local substations, dealing with menial work every day. A series of murders take place before an officer, threatening a town that had been peaceful for 20 years. This series follows a man who realizes that to catch monsters, he must become a monster himself.

name: KABANERI OF THE IRON FORTRESS
description: During the industrial revolution, mankind is threatened by a sudden emergence of undead monsters who can only be killed by piercing their heart through an iron plate. Those bitten become one of them. Called “Kabane,” these monsters exploded in number. The Hinomoto people built fortress stations and barricaded themselves inside. Only steam locomotives, the Hayajiros, can travel between them.(C)KC

name: BABYLON
description: Everyone knows that life is good. But what if that belief was shown to be wrong one day? Don’t miss the long-awaited animated version of Mado Nozaki’s sensational novel, which critics have described as a poison that enters your body when you read it! This story follows Zen Seizaki from the Tokyo District Public Prosecutors Office as he investigates a scandal involving a pharmaceutical company.

name: The Curse Season 1
description: Whitney and Asher are a newlywed couple struggling to bring their vision for eco-conscious housing to the small community of Española. Their efforts are complicated when an eccentrically flawed reality TV producer, Dougie, sees an opportunity in their story. The couple find themselves caught in a mysterious web of ethical and moral gray zones - all while trying to keep their relationship afloat.

name: Paap-O-Meter - Season 1
description: An unusual tale of the intersection of inhabitants of Planet Earth & The Ghost World – Bhoot Lok, Paapometer captures the unique and humorous situations that two companion ghosts – Thakela & Pakela find themselves in.The contrivance – Paapometer, which captures any illicit activity around on Earth, rings everytime the level of ‘Paap’ goes beyond a certain acceptable limit.

name: Builders - Season 1
description: A gang of five selfishly motivated and destructive friends spend their time in a gym and go through various adventures.

name: Monstrous Season -1
description: A giant Buddha statue is unearthed in a small rural town. The mayor believes that it will change the town into a major tourist attraction. However, a catastrophe starts to grow. A centuries-old curse is unleashed from the statue, and it starts to eat up people's souls and make them non-human. Jung Ki-hoon, as archaeologist tries to seek the truth behind the paranormal phenomenon.

name: Taarak Mehta Kka Chhota Chashmah - Season 2
description: Taking forward the 12 year old legacy of television’s most successful comedy show, Tarak Mehta Ka Oolta Chasma, is now the new animation version Tarak Mehta Ka Chota Chasma! Especially designed for the young audiences, the show in its animation avatar, gets, bigger, bolder and funnier!

name: Clique Season 1
description: When Georgia gets drawn into an elite university clique of alpha girls, her friend Holly becomes alarmed by her changing, erratic behaviour, and feels compelled to join - only to find this seductive world is deeply corrupte

name: Siyaasat
description: Based on the book 'The Twentieth Wife' by Indu Sundaresan, Siyaasat is a story of politics, inter-personal conflicts, sabotage, grandeur, power and above all else, the love between Salim and Mehrunissa, Salim's final wife. From their first meeting until their coronations as Jehangir and Nur-Jahan, witness the drama and intrigue that was a part of the royal lifestyle and their romance.

name: Lovestruck High - Season 1
description: Lindsay Lohan narrates Lovestruck High, the reality show which transports a group of UK singles looking for love into their very own High School. At the end of the semester, which couple will be crowned Prom Royalty and win the $100,000 prize?

name: Jim Gaffigan: Dark Pale
description: Considered one of the most prolific and relatable stand-up comedians of today, Jim Gaffigan explores the post Covid emotional landscape in his newest comedy special Dark Pale.

name: Malgudi Days
description: Malgudi Days is an Indian television series based on the eponymous works of R. K. Narayan.Each of the stories portrays a facet of life in Malgudi. The series was directed by Kannada actor and director Shankar Nag. Malgudi Days is a collection of short stories by R. K. Narayan. Each of the stories portrays a facet of life in Village named Malgudi.

name: Fading Gigolo - Season 1
description: Alfonso, a sensitive watchmaker and feminism enthusiast, finds out something that will change his life forever: his father is suddenly back after a heart attack and comes out into the open, telling him that he’s not an antique dealer but a gigolo! After a series of unfortunate events, Alfonso is forced to follow his father’s path.

name: Hightown Season 1
description: Jackie Quiñones, a hard-partying National Marine Fisheries Service agent, has her free-wheeling life thrown into disarray when she discovers a body on the beach – another casualty of Cape Cod’s opioid epidemic. To deal with the trauma, Jackie takes the first steps toward sobriety — until she becomes convinced it’s up to her to solve the murder.

name: KAMEN RIDER BLACK SUN
description: The year is 2022. It is an era of chaos, half a century after the government announced the coexistence of humans and kaijins. Aoi Izumi, a young human rights activist calling for the elimination of discrimination, meets a man named Kotaro Minami, the one called "Black Sun", who is a candidate for the next Creation King.

name: Fairfax - Season 1
description: Fairfax is an irreverent animated comedy following the misadventures of thirteen year-olds Dale, Derica, Benny and Truman, four best friends on a never-ending quest for clout. It’s a modern look at the timeless struggle to be cooler than you are, to fit in while standing out, and what it feels like to wait in line for a pair of sneakers you’re never going to cop.

name: The Unsolved Murder of Beverly Lynn Smith - Season 1
description: A cold case murder spanning over four decades. A friendship born of a love of fishing soon turns sinister. An infamous police tactic. Woven together from first hand accounts and expert interviews, family archives, and rare access to key participants, this documentary series is a winding tale that explores the unrelenting enigma of a search for justice.

name: The Tudors - Season 3
description: Following the execution of Anne Boleyn, King Henry VIII remarries in hopes of having a son as challenges to his authority from both inside and outside the kingdom threaten his hold on England's throne.

name: Fit Check: Confessions of an Ukay Queen Season 1
description: Melanie's dream of making it big in the fashion world draws from her deep interest in ukay fashion and the pain of being abandoned by her own mother. She finds the opportunity when Chris, a fashion executive of a struggling streetwear company, takes notice of her talents. Determined and committed to her cause, Malanie takes on a tough path to success in a world where she is a nobody and a misfit.

name: American Gods, Season 2
description: Season Two finds the battle between Old Gods and New Gods moving inexorably towards crisis point as their destinies collide with those of men. In this strange new world, faith requires terrible sacrifice.

name: Citizen Khan S01
description: The trials and tribulations of a larger-than-life self-appointed Muslim community leader.

name: Mr. Mercedes, Season 2
description: A demented serial killer taunts a retired police detective with a series of lurid letters and emails.

name: The Bridge - Season 2
description: A rusty old coastal tanker navigating the waterway of Öresund suddenly veers off course and heads straight for the Øresund Bridge. The Malmö Coast Guard contacts the tanker but gets no reply. Up on the empty ship bridge, echoes the call of the operator. There is no crew in sight. A man on the Swedish side of the Bridge catches the ship in his binoculars.

name: Lorena - Season 1
description: From Executive Producer Jordan Peele, this four-part docuseries investigates the events of 1993, where Lorena Bobbitt sliced off her husband’s penis after years of abuse. John and Lorena Bobbitt’s stories exploded into a 24-hour news cycle. She became a national joke, her suffering ignored by the male-dominated press. But as John spiraled downward, Lorena found strength in the scars of her ordeal.

name: Operation MBBS - Season 2
description: A year full of laughs, tears and goosebumps with Nishant, Huma & Sakshi. Will they be able to survive this second year of medical college? Here's presenting India's first web series dedicated to the duty and sacrifice by our doctors and frontline warriors.

name: Joko Winterscheidt Presents - The World's Most Dangerous Show - Season 1
description: Joko Winterscheidt takes on one of humanity's biggest challenges: the climate crisis. Joko reaches his limits on this journey, driven to despair by the state of the world. But he also meets people who are fighting for a better, more sustainable world and who give Joko hope.

name: Two and a Half Men: The Complete First Season
description: Charlie Sheen and Jon Cryer star in this Emmy?-nominated comedy about two brothers and a precocious kid. Charlie Harper is a bachelor in paradise - complete with Malibu beach house, overpaid job and an incredibly active dating life.

name: Harmony with A R Rahman Season 1
description: Harmony with A.R Rahman' is a curated exploration of the past and future of Indian music through the eyes of A. R. Rahman. India’s rich musical heritage is viewed through the prism of four specially curated instruments and vocal traditions, selected in order to represent the geographic and historic diversity of the country. The series will examine the traditions, the musicians and the locations.

name: Charitraheen (Hindi) - Season 1
description: Hoichoi Originals presents “Charitraheen”, based on the novel by Sarat Chandra Chattopadhyay, with the twists and turns being much in sync with today’s world.

name: James May: Oh Cook! - Season 2
description: James May is back in the kitchen! This season sees our rookie chef bravely take on delicious yet challenging recipes from across the globe. From Mexico and Japan via 1970s dinner parties and European classics, James shows how anyone can master great dishes with ingredients you can actually buy. And all without the usual television cooking format trickery.

name: Super Bheem - Season 2
description: Super Bheem is the valiant superhero of all the galaxies combined and embarks on many adventurous journeys through mythical lands.

name: Hum Do Teen Chaar
description: With an unemployed and eccentric father, an overworked controlling mother, a phone obsessed daughter and a bookworm son - the Gupta family turn each day into an unpredictable adventure. Watch how things turn around for this happy family.

name: Comedy Island Philippines - Season 1
description: Every 100 years, the best of humanity are chosen to participate in the Centennial Games, vying for the Gift that could change the world. Only problem is the ones who arrived are clueless celebrities who have no idea what’s going on. But when the Gift suddenly goes missing, they must unmask the thief, or else, be stuck on the island forever.

name: History's Greatest Escapes with Morgan Freeman - Season 1
description: Interviews and re-creations bring some of history's most daring jailbreaks to life, detailing every step of the way, including the inmates' meticulous plans and the manhunts that followed.

name: Unforgettable, Season 3
description: A chance meeting puts a female ex-cop in touch with her former boyfriend, a New York City police detective, who convinces her to use her extraordinary memory to solve crimes.

name: Dudes Season 1
description: Billuka is a renowned Fintech company created and managed altogether by Julian and his friends Ricardo, Simón, Santiago, Tomas, Daniel and Mafe. On the other hand, Antonia, daughter of a very important businessman, arrives to Colombia in hopes to make a fresh start. When Julian meets Antonia is love at first sight. Later, Julian entangles himself on a series of conflicts between love and business.

name: Babylon Berlin: Series 3
description: Based on the novels by Volker Kutscher and starring Volker Bruch and Liv Lisa Fries, 'Babylon Berlin' returns for a third, thrilling series which sees the decadent city in turmoil as it undergoes cultural, political and economic change and lurches towards the 1929 crash.

name: American Gods Season 3 – International Release
description: Shadow attempts to break away and assert himself as his own man, setting roots down in the idyllic snowy town of Lakeside, Wisconsin. There he’ll uncover a dark secret while exploring questions of his own divinity. Guided on this spiritual journey by the gods of his black ancestors, the Orisha, Shadow must decide exactly who he is—a god seeking veneration, or a man in service of the “we.”

name: Cheer Up (Telugu) - Season 1
description: A renowned college cheerleading squad is about to go under. But love and mysteries occur within the team

name: Mid Wicket Tales With Naseeruddin Shah
description: Hosted by the veteran actor, 'Mid Wicket Tales with Naseeruddin Shah' explores the many interesting untold stories of Indian cricket. With personal accounts of their experiences from cricketers like Tiger Pataudi and Bishan Singh Bedi, anecdotes from personalities like Shashi Tharoor, Charu Sharma and Sharmila Tagore, re-enactments, and trivia,  it's a must-watch for all cricket lovers.

name: Shaktimaan
description: Shaktimaan Is First Indian Superhero. He Is Depicted As A Human Who Has Attained Superhuman Strength And Power Through Deep Meditation And Attaining Control Over Five Elements Of Life. He Fights Against Tamraj Kilvish, Who Is The Living Embodiment Of The Evil And Dark Forces Of The World And Shaktimaan's Nemesis.

name: Karakuri Circus
description: After inheriting the family fortune, eleven-year-old Masaru Saiga is targeted by kidnappers armed with bizarre and deadly puppets. He escapes once aided by circus employee Narumi Kato, but the kidnappers soon catch up with them. Just when all seems lost, the two are saved by the mysterious Shirogane who wields her own marionette. From then on, the trio’s fates become inexorably intertwined...

name: Ghosts S01
description: A cash-strapped young couple inherit a grand country house, only to find it is both falling apart and teeming with the ghosts of former inhabitants.

name: Couple Goals - Season 4
description: The show revolves around up's and down's of a couple's relationship. We follow them through their struggles of ambition, love and insecurities. The show starts on a note of a competition where the Ayush unintentionally ruins Jenny's performance. As story follows, we see them go through intensities of growth and downfalls. But eventually they both part ways to follow their love for their art.

name: Hello(Hindi) - Season 1
description: The festival of Durga Puja becomes memorable for Nandita when suddenly she receives an MMS from an unknown number, that turns her life upside down.

name: Spartacus Season 2
description: On the heels of the bloody escape from the House of Batiatus, the gladiator rebellion continues, striking fear into the heart of the Roman Republic. Spartacus is presented the choice of satisfying his personal need for vengeance against the man that condemned his wife to slavery and eventual death or making the larger sacrifice necessary to keep his budding army from breaking apart.

name: We Are Newcastle United - Season 1
description: Having spent over £300 million to buy the club, appointed a new Head Coach, Eddie Howe, and made a bold statement of intent by signing several big name players, fans' expectations are rocketing and the new owners and Head Coach have much to do to transform the club's fortunes. The series follows life at the club both on and off the pitch. New Episodes available on Fridays!

name: Last Light (Season 1)
description: Based on the bestselling novel, this action packed dystopian thriller centers around a family whose lives are changed forever when oil supplies get contaminated by an infectious agent, causing society to implode in the face of global disaster. Matthew Fox and Joanne Froggatt lead an impressive international cast in a sweeping international saga that spans several continents.

name: Scum's Wish
description: Hopeless love... Painful love... Unrequited love... Are they really all that beautiful? In her second year in high school, Hanabi Yasuraoka is hopelessly in love with the wrong person. Someone she's willing to do anything to be with, even if it means hurting the people she cares about. This is a love story both pure and disturbed.(C)MY/SQEX,S

name: Bestseller - Season 1
description: Celebrated novelist Tahir Wazir who is facing writer's block, meets budding writer Meetu Mathur. She is a huge fan who seeks his guidance. Desperate Tahir decides to use her story for his next novel. Ad film assistant Parth is planning something vicious to destroy Tahir and his close ones. Will he succeed? Will Tahir be able to write his next bestseller? Everything unfolds in 8 chapters!

name: THE IDOLM@STER.KR - Season 1
description: Only those who survive can make their debut as a girl group! The series follows the story of 11 girls as they fiercely compete and undergo vigorous training to become idol stars.(C) BANDAI NAMCO Entertainment Inc & IMX, Inc.

name: Season 01
description: In 1969, while a cultural revolution swept through the free world, there was still one place that refused to change with the times: newsrooms. Good Girls Revolt follows a group of young female researchers at "News of the Week," who ask to be treated fairly. Their revolutionary request sparks convulsive changes and upends marriages, careers, sex lives, love lives, and friendships.

name: Mani Muthu Season 2
description: Story of Mani and Muthu

name: El Presidente- Season 1
description: International Emmy® Awards nominee (Drama Series). Sergio Jadue, a lowly director of a small-town soccer club in Chile, unexpectedly finds himself at the head of the Chilean soccer association. Drunk with power, he becomes the protégé of soccer godfather Julio Grondona, as well as the FBI’s key to undoing the largest corruption scheme in the world of soccer.

name: Tempted (Telugu) - Season 1
description: Love is just a game for Chaebol heir who agrees to a petty bet with his friends to seduce a college student - until he starts to fall for her.

name: Swayamvaram Season 3
description: Rakhi meet her bosom friend Sarika for the first time after they left college. Rakhi was shocked to find Sarika's life is an utter failure since she marrid her college lover Jose.

name: Doctor Who, Series 5
description: Matt Smith sets out as the Eleventh Doctor with a brand new TARDIS and a feisty new companion in Amy Pond. His enemies are never far behind him, including old nemeses the Daleks and Weeping Angels.

name: Fauji - Hindi
description: This is a drama series about commandos joining the army training school. Their life, their pranks and their punishments are show-cased through various characters of the serial.

name: Tale of the Nine Tailed 1938
description: A K-fantasy action unfolds as the Nine-tailed fox (played by Lee Dong-wook) makes a crash landing in the year 1938, an era of chaos, and he struggles to return to the present.

name: Parnashavarir Shaap (Bengali) - Season 1
description: A tranquil vacation of four friends at a hillside village takes a sinister turn, when they unwittingly incur the wrath of an ancient deity, Devi Parnashavari. Renowned ocultist, Bhaduri Moshai, is sought out to ward off the goddess' menacing curse that threatens to engulf them all!

name: Murder In The Hills (Bengali) - Season 1
description: The seemingly normal death of a legendary movie star in Darjeeling threatens to expose the seedy underbelly of the serene hill station.

name: Gaurav Kapoor - Season 1
description: Gaurav Kapoor

name: Power - Season 1
description: James "Ghost" St. Patrick has it all: a beautiful wife, a Manhattan penthouse, and New York's hottest nightclub. But he's also the kingpin of the city's most lucrative drug network, causing many problems. Once you're in, can you ever get out?

name: DCI Banks S01
description: Stephen Tompkinson and Andrea Lowe star as the tenacious and stubborn Chief Inspector Alan Banks and the feisty and headstrong Detective Sergeant Annie Cabbot in three thrilling crime stories.

name: Mobaroknama (Bengali) - Season 1
description: Once an accomplished lawyer, Mobarok had retired after a case had rocked his moral foundation. Suddenly, a sensational case jolts the now-jaded man. Even after knowing that defeat in the case is inevitable, Mobarok returns to court because victory there is the only way to atone for his past mistake!

name: Honey Bunny Ka Jholmaal - Season 2
description: In a cozy house in the town owned by a young lady there lives 2 cats, a parrot and a watch dog who are the sweetest and the meekest pets ever but the moment the young lady leaves home, the cats becomes super mischievous, the parrot becomes super talkative and the poor dog goes super frantic.

name: Wallander
description: Kenneth Branagh plays a troubled detective in this acclaimed crime drama set in Sweden.

name: Lost Essence Of India - Season 2
description: This series showcases the unexplored and hidden gems of pristine locations throughout India.

name: LOL: Australia - Season 1
description: Hosted by Rebel Wilson, 10 of Australia’s finest comedians battle it out to see who can keep a straight face while simultaneously trying to make their opponents laugh. Comedians who laugh will be eliminated one-by-one, until a single comedian remains. With $100,000 on the line, who will Rebel crown the Last One Laughing?.

name: Work Later, Drink Now S2
description: Ahn So-Hee, Kang Ji-goo, and Han Ji-Yeon are three single ladies whose friendship blossoms as they share drinks after work and discuss about everything from their jobs to their romantic relationships. They experience many enjoyable and surprising events while they drink. These three ladies will live their lives with openness and honesty, sharing common experiences of women in their 30's.

name: Naked and Afraid XL - Season 1
description: 10 Naked and Afraid alumni are stranded together for 40 days in the wilderness without clothing, food, or shelter.

name: Lore  - Season 2
description: From an executive producer of The Walking Dead and an executive producer of The Exorcist, this season of the critically acclaimed anthology series will explore real-life frightening and disturbing tales that give rise to modern-day myths and legends. Season two will feature new tales based on the award-winning podcast as well as original stories not yet available in podcast form.

name: Man's World - Season 1
description: What if women treated men, the way men treat women? It is a story about walking a mile in their shoes, in that world. Kiran, the protagonist, believes the world is really unfair to men. Fed up, he prays for the world to flip and for men and women to interchange places. As they say, be careful what you wish for.

name: Eena Meena Deeka
description: Eena Meena Deeka is the story of a constant chase between a cunning hungry fox and three chicks Eena, Meena & Deeka. The fox is forever on the prowl of the chicks & the chicks are always ready to foil his plans. Angry and defeated, the fox is even more determined to get his targets, with each consequent failure.

name: Chandigarh Wale - Season 1
description: Charan and Dimple move to Chandigarh to lead a better life, but they are unable to do so as they are constantly annoyed by the numerable unwanted guests who keep visiting them one after another.

name: Love Kills: Shabnam aur Saleem - Amroha Hatyakand - Season 1
description: This hard-hitting investigative series looks at the world of grisly murders in India. These stories of revenge, jealously and greed are broken down to reveal what actually happened to lead to a gruesome killing.

name: This is Football - Season 1
description: An emotionally-charged, six-part documentary, exploring football’s extraordinary impact on the world. From the streets of Delhi to the fields of post-war Rwanda to the pitches of the Champions League, this globe-spanning series tells a unique story of the game and its power to unite countries, inspire generations and captivate billions.

name: Anna - Season 1
description: The story of a woman who ends up living a completely different life due to a petty lie.

name: Unforgettable Season 02
description: 13EME RUE Carrie Wells, a former police detective, has a rare ability to remember virtually everything she experiences including detailed visual recall. She returns to police work and uses her ability to solve crimes.

name: Anni: The Honeymoon Murder - Season 1
description: Anni Dewani's murder in South Africa while on honeymoon with her husband Shrien becomes one of the country's most infamous and mysterious crimes. With testimony from the lawyers, police, and those involved, Anni's family wants to know why she had to die.

name: Making The Cut - Season 1
description: In this first season of Making the Cut, Heidi Klum and Tim Gunn take 12 established designers around the world from New York to Paris to Tokyo, as they compete to become the next global fashion brand. Each week, winning looks will be available to buy on Amazon in the Making the Cut store, and the last designer standing will receive one million dollars to invest in their brand.

name: Upload - Season 1
description: From the Emmy-winning Greg Daniels (The Office, Parks & Rec) comes a hilarious new sci-fi comedy. In the future people can upload their consciousness to a luxurious digital afterlife. When party boy Nathan gets uploaded to a virtual resort he meets the down-to-earth Nora who starts as his customer service “angel”, but becomes so much more as she helps him find friendship, love and purpose.

name: Weightlifting Fairy Kim Bok-Joo (Telugu) - Season 1
description: Kim Bok-joo, a weightlifter, gets attracted to a fitness doctor and is even ready to lose weight for him. However, her childhood friend, a talented swimmer, inspires her to achieve her dreams.

name: Season 14
description: In the 14th season of `NCIS' Special Agents Leroy Jehro Gibbs, Timothy McGee and Ellie Bishop return to investigate complex crimes. They examine the case of a missing MI6 Officer, and go in pursuit of a hacker following a high-level cyber attack.

name: Breathe: Into The Shadows
description: A 6-year old girl is kidnapped by a mysterious masked man, who demands an unusual ransom. To save his daughter, Dr. Avinash Sabharwal must kill someone! Meanwhile, Kabir Sawant's journey continues in the hostile environment of the Delhi Crime branch. Lies, deceit and mind games begin when Kabir is given charge of the investigation, and meets Avinash. How far will Avinash go to save his daughter?

name: Classic Popeye
description: Popeye is one of the most popular cartoon characters of all time. This spunky but loveable spinach-eating sailor continues to delight young and old with his comic adventures, and  the entire gang is around to provide plenty of rousing fun and action: Olive Oyl, Swee'Pea, Wimpy and Bluto.

name: Shikaari - Season 2
description: The only way out is to kill or get killed, as the old rival is now back, intending to see the downfall of Shikaaris.

name: The Romanoffs - Season 1
description: From the creator of Mad Men, The Romanoffs is a contemporary anthology series set around the globe featuring eight separate stories about people who believe themselves to be descendants of the Russian royal family. Starring Aaron Eckhart, Diane Lane, Isabelle Huppert, Christina Hendricks, John Slattery, Amanda Peet, Jack Huston, Kathryn Hahn, Noah Wyle, Paul Reiser, Andrew Rannells and more.

name: New Tricks S09
description: Detective Superintendent Sandra Pullman is back heading up her team of retired detectives who don't always do things by the book but always get results.

name: Sneaky Pete - Season 2
description: On the verge of starting fresh, Marius (Giovanni Ribisi) is dragged back into the role of Pete Murphy when two thugs—believing he’s Pete—threaten to kill the Bernhardts if he doesn’t take them to Pete’s estranged mother and the millions she stole from their employer. Now Marius must tread a dangerous line to find her and protect the family, all while keeping up the Pete con.

name: LOL: Last One Laughing Colombia - Season 1
description: For the first time in Colombia, LOL opens its doors to 10 of the best comedians to compete against each other to win the LOL trophy while they dare to make comedy free of censorship and limits. In this crazy extreme experiment, comedians will reveal much more than their repertoire of jokes. What will be their challenge? Make each of their opponents laugh while keeping a straight face.

name: 21 Jump Street
description: Fresh-faced undercover cops head back to high school on the hunt for criminals in this riveting crime drama starring screen icon Johnny Depp.

name: How The Universe Works - Season 3
description: How the Universe Works shows you how the cosmos is designed, built, and actually works.
